### Hello
Hi there. I'm Kristie and I'm a senior studying biomedical engineering at Duke. I'm interested in neural engineering and neural prosthetics. Outside of class, I enjoy building things, climbing trees, petting dogs, running, humming, cheering on the Blue Devils in Cameron, star gazing, and eating ice cream.
